Package it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema

Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.schema.Session
  • public class Session
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an implementation of an OLAP query session. A session belongs to a profile, and is created by a template (which generates the session's query list).
